Module kivakit.core
Package com.telenav.kivakit.core.collections.map

Class BaseMap<Key,Value>

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.kivakit.core.collections.map.BaseMap<Key,Value>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Emptiness, Sized, SpaceLimited, Map<Key,Value>
Direct Known Subclasses:
BaseIndexedMap, BaseStringMap, CacheMap, MultiMap, MultiSet, ObjectMap, TwoWayMap
public class BaseMap<Key,Value> extends Object implements Map<Key,Value>, SpaceLimited
A base class for bounded maps which wraps a Map implementation. The following methods are added to the base functionality:
  • get(Object, Object) - Typesafe version of getOrDefault(Object, Object)
  • getOrCreate(Object) - Creates missing values using onCreateValue(Object)
  • put(Object, Object, Object) - Puts the given value. Uses the default value if the value is null
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
